==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Catalan
<hw>Cat"a*lan</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to
Catalonia.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>A native or inhabitant of
Catalonia; also, the language of Catalonia.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><mcol><col><b>Catalan furnace</b></col>, <col><b>Catalan
forge</b></col></mcol> <fld>(Metal.)</fld>, <cd>a kind of furnace for
producing wrought iron directly from the ore. It was formerly much used,
esp. in Catalonia, and is still used in some parts of the United States
and elsewhere.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>catalase</ent>⟦br⟧
